{"tid":2249513,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"自殺勝地 東堤小築兩男女燒炭昏迷　送院搶救","createTime":"2020-10-19T11:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T11:25:32.000Z","uid":56810,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9a57f18fa23240809e428a04e0da8f692e7d1e39","tid":2249513,"uid":56810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:24:59.000Z","msg":"長洲東堤小築又揭發雙人燒炭。今日(19日)傍晚6時許，有居民途經其中一單位門外時，聞到單位內傳出燒炭氣味，恐有人發生意外，遂報警求助。<br />\n消防接報到場破門而入，發現一男一女昏迷倒臥單位內，兩人身旁有一盤燒過的炭，懷疑他們燒炭自殺，立即將他們送往長洲醫院搶救，警方在現場展開調查。"},{"pid":"1e68114e4ebce5f9f82b5ee929df2da5b24f3cbd","tid":2249513,"uid":67329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T11:25:32.000Z","msg":"2020<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}